        <p><span class="text-stone/60">[CALIBRATING]</span> Capillary fluctuation: <span class="text-amber-bright">ACTIVE</span></p>

        <div class="divider-amber my-4"></div>

        <p class="text-ivory">
          <span class="text-amber">&gt;</span> You're in a desert, walking along in the sand, when all of a sudden you look down and see a tortoise. It's crawling toward you...
        </p>
        <p class="text-ivory">
          <span class="text-amber">&gt;</span> You reach down and flip the tortoise over on its back. The tortoise lays on its back, its belly baking in the hot sun, beating its legs trying to turn itself over, but it can't. Not without your help.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ivory">
          <span class="text-amber">&gt;</span> But you're not helping. Why is that?
        </p>

        <div class="divider-amber my-4"></div>

        <p>
          <span class="text-stone/60">[ANALYZING]</span>
          <span class="text-amber">SUBJECT RESPONSE:
            <span class="inline-block w-2 h-4 bg-amber/80 ml-1" style="animation: amber-pulse 0.8s step-end infinite;"></span>
          </span>
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-amber/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-stone/50 tracking-wider">
            VK SESSION: <span class="text-amber/60">VK-2026-0847</span>
          </p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-stone/50 tracking-wider">
            EXAMINER: <span class="text-amber/60">HOLDEN, D.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-stone/50 tracking-wider">
            STATUS: <span class="text-amber">AWAITING INPUT</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA buttons -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary text-center">BEGIN VK ASSESSMENT</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-secondary text-center">REQUEST EXEMPTION</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Legal disclaimer -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-stone/40 tracking-wider max-w-lg mx-auto">
        ALL PERSONNEL MUST SUBMIT TO VOIGHT-KAMPFF TESTING PER CORPORATE POLICY TI-4774.
        REFUSAL IS GROUNDS FOR IMMEDIATE TERMINATION AND INVESTIGATION.
        REPLICANTS DISCOVERED THROUGH VK TESTING ARE SUBJECT TO RETIREMENT.
